Heartbroken actress, Jessica Nkosi found herself as a talk of the twitter streets this morning after she exposed her cheating baby daddy. Jessica and TK Dlamini welcomed their 1st child together last year and earlier this year their relationship was already hogging headlines, alleging that they have broken up. Jessica took to Instagram stories to reveal that indeed TK has been cheating and she thanked her followers for helping her with the 'receipts'. “To you who is seeing the father of my child behind my back; you are free to be with him fully now… *no more hiding* lol. Enjoy babe,” wrote Nkosi in her Instagram story. 